Package com.atakmap.android.cot.importer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MapItemImporter.NotificationFilter
    Callback interface to allow external components to determines whether or not an imported item should post a notification.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CASEVACMarkerImporter
    Importer for CASEVAC markers
    CotEventTypeImporter
    CoT event importer that filters by CoT type
    CotImporterManager
    Import manager optimized for CoT imports
    DIPMarkerImporter
    Importer for Jumpmaster DIPs Note: Although Jumpmaster is a plugin, users without the plugin loaded should still be able to see DIPs on the map, so the importer is in core
    FriendlyMarkerImporter
    Importer for friendly markers Includes extra logic to deal with contact friendlies
    LegacyMarkerImporter
    Importer for legacy markers that should not follow the default marker logic
    MapItemImporter
    CoT importer specifically for items on the map
    MarkerImporter
    CoT importer specifically for markers Most of this implementation was moved from CotMapAdapter
    SPIMarkerImporter
    Importer for SPI markers
    SpotMapImporter
    Importer for spot map markers and labels
    UserIconMarkerImporter
    Importer for user icon markers
